-Listen to me.

556
00:38:45,440 --> 00:38:48,000
But no chemical substance will do that.

557
00:38:49,960 --> 00:38:51,199
And I'm scared...

558
00:38:52,480 --> 00:38:55,199
that you'll keep on trying

559
00:38:56,800 --> 00:38:59,119
until you end up joining her
before your time.

560
00:39:01,920 --> 00:39:04,400
And it's a bit too early

561
00:39:05,320 --> 00:39:08,639
to tell which of our gods is right
about the afterlife.

562
00:39:10,719 --> 00:39:12,079
Don't you think?

563
00:39:28,280 --> 00:39:29,280
Guzmán!

564
00:39:33,400 --> 00:39:34,400
