631
00:45:04,320 --> 00:45:07,960
No, just enough to do
what you've been wanting to do.

632
00:45:08,039 --> 00:45:09,079
And I have, too.

633
00:45:15,920 --> 00:45:17,960
-Good night, Guzmán.
-Nadia...

634
00:45:43,239 --> 00:45:44,480
What's going on with you?

635
00:45:45,280 --> 00:45:47,000
